frontmatter.title: Just because I can doesn't mean I should
frontmatter.description: This Valentine's Day, I reflect on the biggest lesson my past relationship taught me: just because I can, doesn’t mean I should. Independence is great, and it's necessary to create a healthy interdependent relationship. But that doesn't mean doing it all.
